WEBVTT

00:00.129 --> 00:03.739
In the next few months, the motion picture industry and theater owners...

00:04.491 --> 00:07.460
...will be bringing you a series of messages like the one you just saw.

00:08.602 --> 00:10.219
I don't think anybody will miss the point.

00:11.371 --> 00:13.078
The thrill can kill.

00:14.200 --> 00:17.117
The drug dealers need to know that we want them...

00:17.227 --> 00:20.181
...out of our schools, neighborhoods and our lives.

00:21.041 --> 00:24.775
And the only way to do that is to take the customers away from the product.

00:25.717 --> 00:28.947
Say no to drugs and say yes to life.

